.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fnetanyahu-indicates-israel-open-to-ending-gaza-war-if-hostages-are-released-and-other-conditions%2Famp_articleshow%2F121248923.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%2033%20and%20I%20have%204%20roommates.%20The%20rent%20fits%20my%20budget%20and%20I%20love%20the%20company%2C%20but%20sometimes%20I'd%20prefer%20to%20live%20alone.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20with%20three%20of%20her%20roommates%20in%20the%20backyard%20of%20their%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6827afdec6ad288d14813a4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20left%2C%20lives%20with%20four%20roommates%20in%20a%20five-bedroom%20house.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mary%20Beth%20Skylis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20live%20in%20a%20house%20with%20four%20roommates%2C%20and%20we're%20all%20in%20our%2030s.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20are%20some%20frustrating%20things%20about%20my%20living%20situation%2C%20but%20there%20are%20pros%2C%20too.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20fits%20my%20budget%2C%20and%20the%20company%20is%20nice%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20love%20having%20to%20fight%20for%20fridge%20space.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20once%20a%20week%2C%20I%20down%20my%20coffee%20and%20sprint%20to%20the%20bathroom%2C%20moments%20later%2C%20only%20to%20find%20the%20door%20locked.%20Someone%20beat%20me%20to%20it.%20I%20pace%20in%20the%20hallway%20for%20a%20minute%20or%20two%2C%20imagining%20that%20they%20must%20be%20almost%20done.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20time%20is%20not%20on%20my%20side%2C%20so%20I%20take%20two%20flights%20of%20stairs%20to%20the%20basement%20to%20do%20my%20business%20in%20the%20spider-infested%20half%20bathroom%2C%20ripe%20with%20annoyance.%20On%20my%20long%20climb%20back%20up%20to%20my%20bedroom%2C%20I%20ask%20myself%20why%20I%20live%20in%20a%20five-bedroom%2C