ges%2Fhow-much-rent-can-i-afford%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eplaces%20that%20fit%20my%20budget%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239c9b5f5-2dcd-424c-8640-379c8c1c27d4%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20thought%20my%20life%20would%20look%20different%20by%20this%20point%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20had%20asked%20me%20where%20I'd%20be%20by%20the%20time%20I%20was%2033%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20would%20have%20told%20you%20I'd%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsix-months-traveling-just-backpack-europe-trip-packing-tips-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eliving%20out%20of%20a%20backpack%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20somewhere%20in%20Europe%20or%20South%20America%20with%20a%20smile%20plastered%20on%20my%20face.%20I%20thought%20that%20right%20now%2C%20I'd%20be%20traveling%20around%2C%20filthy%2C%20with%20a%20map%20in%20one%20hand%20and%20a%20baguette%20in%20the%20other.%20And%20for%20much%20of%20the%20year%2C%20I%20do%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20live%20this%20way%20(albeit%20it's%20usually%20an%20espresso%20instead%20of%20a%20baguette%2C%20and%20a%20smartphone%20instead%20of%20a%20map).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20I%20didn't%20realize%20all%20those%20years%20ago%2C%20while%20I%20was%20dreaming%20up%20my%20ideal%20life%2C%20is%20that%20sometimes%20I'd%20crave%20the%20comfort%20of%20a%20home%2C%20too.%20I%20couldn't%20have%20predicted%20that%20after%20a%20few%20weeks%20on%20the%20road%2C%20I'd%20grow%20weary%20of%20red-eye%20flights%20and%20begin%20to%20crave%20my%20bed%2C%20a%20familiar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ultra-processed-foods-impact-your-body-calories-weight-gain-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eultra-processed%20diet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20my%20guitar.%20And%20I%20definitely%20couldn't%20have%